A custom Adobe Flex Spark component.

This component can be used as a loading placeholder when loading remote data.

Usage:

You can set an optional loading title which will be displayed along with the animated throbber.

<container:LoadingPane skinClass="shinydesign.skin.LoadingPaneSkin" id="loadingPanel" height="300" width="400" loadingTitle="Loading Demo Data">
...anything you like here
</container>